narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: Learned about RELION, the computational program used for cryoEM data analysis and also evaluated data in CryoET, single molecule CryoEM and experimental techniques.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: Sometimes the topics discussed in the morning were too advanced for beginners. Next years the professors should explain the basics a bit better
Very good course, some lectures could be less in depth, sometimes following them was very confusing.

comments: Yes, student should have previous knowledge of the technique
